Provides a SPARQL testing framework that can be used for testing various SPARQL operations (queries, updates and GSP operations) and extended to test arbitrary operations if desired.

Package Description
net.sf.sparql.benchmarking.util  

Provides a SPARQL testing framework that can be used for testing various SPARQL operations (queries, updates and GSP operations) and extended to test arbitrary operations if desired.

The framework can be used to test both remote SPARQL services and to test against in-memory datasets (or a mixture of both).
